column5: Just got an email with this picture of the new world record piranha. It doesnt really look too much like a piranha to me. What do you guys think?
Old picture, not a piranha. It's a congo fish.
And Crazyhook wins the cupie doll! WTG Jamie!
TIGER FISH!  DANG I'm slow on the draw 2nite...
Tiger,congo or Piranha.... that is one mean lookin fish. I dont want to be swimming anywhere in the water where this fish lives.
Did ANYONE notice the fellow is not wearing a LINDY glove. TSK TSK!
It is drying on the clothes line, you can see some orange and grey right behind his head.
I heard it was caught in Rainy lake LOL!
